    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073470/extras/1791bb48fccb48041b559fd32d140c13.poster.avif?t=1728347960\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073470/extras/1791bb48fccb48041b559fd32d140c13.webm?t=1728347960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073470/extras/1791bb48fccb48041b559fd32d140c13.mp4?t=1728347960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这是一款充满挑战和策略的像素风格闯关游戏。在这个充满神秘和冒险的世界里，你将化身为勇敢的冒险者，穿越层层关卡，通过商店购买强力装备，不同装备组合搭配，来打败BOSS，最终实现令人惊叹的7万亿输出。<br><strong>游戏特色</strong>：<br>像素风格的精美画面： 经典的像素艺术风格，带你重温怀旧的游戏时光。<br>装备组合策略： 数百种不同的武器和防具可以在商店中购买，自由搭配，创造最适合你的战斗策略。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073470/extras/d0bdd41d7910c5660f2cf550f6d70a52.poster.avif?t=1728347960\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073470/extras/d0bdd41d7910c5660f2cf550f6d70a52.webm?t=1728347960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073470/extras/d0bdd41d7910c5660f2cf550f6d70a52.mp4?t=1728347960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏玩法：<br>闯关冒险： 出战你阵营中的勇者，击败敌人，收集战利品。<br>商店购买装备： 在商店中购买各种装备，根据不同阵容，灵活搭配装备，制定最佳策略。<br>策略战斗： 每个BOSS都有其独特的debuff，选择合适的装备或者策略，以最有效的方式击败他们。<br>逐步提升输出： 通过不断挑战和优化装备组合，提升你的输出能力，向着7万亿的惊人输出目标迈进。",
